title: DDFP 370: Jarvis Landry
itunes:title: DDFP 370: Jarvis Landry
description:
Shek and Handsome Hank discuss the recent deals signed before the franchise tag deadline, including Dez Bryant’s and Demaryius Thomas' long-term contracts (5:04). The guys are then joined by Miami Dolphins wide receiver Jarvis Landry (22:11) to discuss a range of football topics while Shek hones his catching skills.
